quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  19,83,Ana ngankuiona yanti Uwwe tukugatumisyaga mashetani pa achimakafili gagakwakwembelechesyaga kusyene (kutenda yakusakala)
  19,84,"Basi ngasintenda chitema pa ŵanganyao (kuti apedwe ilagasyo mwachitema), chisimu Uwwe tukuŵa tulinkwaŵalanjila ŵanganyao chiŵalanjilo (chamasiku gao, pachigakwanapo tuchapa ilagasyo)"
  19,85,"Lisiku lyatuchasonganganya ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) ulendo wa kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ali m’mikutula jekwele mu yakwela"
  19,86,Ni tuchasakula akuleŵa wa ku Jahannama ali ni njota (mpela yaikasatiji pakusakulidwa ilango yanjota wakukumwa mesi)
  19,87,Ngasakola machili gakuchondelela ikaŵeje jwapochele chilanga (cha lusa) kuumila kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji
  19,88,"Ŵanganyao ni akutiji: “(Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji alitendele mwanache.”"
  19,89,Chisimu pamasile pam’biche nacho chindu chakunyalaya kusyene (pa yankuŵechetayi)
  19,90,"Mawunde gakusigalaga panandi kuti gapasuchepasuche ni maloŵego, nombe litaka ganjikaganjika, nombe matumbi kugwa ni katikakatika"
  19,91,Ligongo lyakunnambuchisya (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji kuti jwana mwanache
  19,92,Soni nganiiŵa yakuŵajilwa kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji kulitendela mwanache
  19,93,Pangali jwalijose jwaali kumawunde ni petaka ikaŵeje chijuchiyika kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji juli kapolo
  19,94,"Chisimu pamasile paŵakusenye ŵanganyao pakwamanya chenene, ni ŵaŵalasile chiŵalanjilo chakwana"
  19,95,Soni ŵosope ŵeneo tachim’bichilila (Allah) lisiku lya Kiyama jikajika
  19,96,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji tachaŵichila ŵanganyao chinonyelo"
  19,97,"Basi chisimu tujijepepesye jele (Qur’aniji) m’chiŵecheto chenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), kuti mwasengwasye najo ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah), ni kwatetela najo ŵandu ŵamakani"
  19,98,Ana jilingwa mwa mikutula jatwajijonasile paujo pao? Ana pana jwalijose jwankum’bona (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) mwa jamanjao kapena kupikana nswakanyo wakwe